{% doc %}
  @prompt
    I want you to generate a complete Shopify section (Liquid + HTML + CSS) for my brand GlowFest.  
    The section should be inspired by the design and layout style of siaasoo.uk — clean, modern, wellness-focused, premium aesthetics.
    
    SECTION CONTENT & STRUCTURE:
    
    1. HERO AREA
    - Title: “GlowFest — Professional Relief, At Home”
    - Subtitle: “Inspired by clinic-grade therapy, designed for everyday life. GlowFest brings deep, therapist-like muscle relief with heat therapy and adaptive pressure.”
    - Button: “Shop GlowFest”
    - Layout: text on the left, two vertical images on the right (image pickers in Shopify customizer)
    
    2. FEATURES (3 columns)
    Each feature should include an icon (image picker), a title, and a short description:
    - Feature 1: “Bionic Hand” — “Deep, realistic kneading inspired by expert therapists.”
    - Feature 2: “Proprietary Chip” — “Adaptive pressure and optimized performance.”
    - Feature 3: “Red-Light Heat” — “Soothing warmth that boosts circulation.”
    
    3. STORY SECTION
    - Left side: 1 image (image picker)
    - Right side: Title “Why GlowFest?”
    - Paragraph text + bullet list
    
    DESIGN REQUIREMENTS:
    - Clean, minimal, premium design similar to siaasoo.uk
    - Colors: white background, soft neutrals, green accent #2f7a46
    - Typography: modern sans-serif (Inter-style)
    - Rounded corners, soft shadows, large spacing, wellness aesthetic
    - Fully responsive (mobile-first)
    - Two-column layouts must stack on mobile
    - No JavaScript, HTML + CSS only
    
    TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS:
    - Must be a valid Shopify section (.liquid file)
    - All images must be editable via the theme editor (schema → image_picker)
    - All texts must be editable via the theme editor (schema → text or richtext settings)
    - CSS must be included inside the section (no external files)
    - Must include a proper schema JSON at the bottom
    - Must be ready to paste into /sections/about-glowfest.liquid
    
    DELIVERABLE:
    → Provide the **FULL Shopify section code** (Liquid + HTML + CSS + Schema).
    
{% enddoc %}
